Package: bistablehistory
Title: Cumulative History for Bistable Perceptual Rivalry
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alexander",
           family = "Pastukhov",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "pastukhov.alexander@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8738-8591"))
Description: Estimates cumulative history for time-series for continuously
    viewed bistable perceptual rivalry displays. Assumes negative exponential 
    growth/decay of the history as a function time and perceptually dominant
    state. Supports Gamma, log normal, exponentially modulate Gaussian, and 
    normal distribution families. Currently can include a single random 
    and/or single fixed effect.
License: `use_gpl3_license()`
